	<h3>Comfy looking couches! Any rules there?</h3>
	<p>Nope - part of the common space, they are for everyone's use and enjoyment, and fall into the same category as any other common resource, meaning: we all use it, so we all take good care of it!</p>
	
	<h3>Where is my mail?</h3>
	<p>Directly next to the reception desk is a nifty array of cubbies, neatly labeled with your company's name, where all of your mail/ small packages will always await you. If you receive something oddly large, it will be in that general area as well, so ask at reception, and we will be sure to tell you which is your new poster print of David Hasselhoff.</p>
	
